        <list id="id1170658503815" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Do you also remember?</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id6643307">The INVERSE (reverse calculation) of subtraction is ADDITION.</para>
        <para id="id7766756">If you therefore want to check a subtraction sum, you can add.</para>
        <para id="id7507203">3. Let’s practise your skills in mental arithmetic again! Subtract the following as quickly as possible. If you know your place values (refer to Learning Unit 1) it will be child’s play. </para>
        <para id="id6598362">2.1  17 – 9 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id1170663010838">2.2  37 – 9 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id1170659995606">2.3  97 – 50 = _________________</para>
        <para id="id1170652711674">2.4  97 – 57 = _________________</para>
