    <section id="id1170652480870">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id2779876"><emphasis>Learning Outcome 1: </emphasis>The learner will be able to recognise, describe and represent numbers and their relationships, and to count, estimate, calculate and check with competence and confidence in solving problems.</para>
      <para id="id1170652518821"><emphasis>Assessment Standard 1.9:</emphasis> We know this when the learner performs mental calculations.</para>
